citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:15 PM on
24-AUG-17.
The inspector spoke to an employee who stated that the licensee was out-of-town and would not be home today.
